channel.title: Cache Editor Problem
channel.description:
Hey,
I wanted to edit my cache of my client but I could not get the cache editor working, When i downloaded there was only a source folder and no bin folder, so it was not compiled. I made a compiler.bat and a run.bat but still dont understand what the problem is, because the compiler gives me this error:
[code] Error: Could not find or load main class bin.alex.Main Press any key to continue . . . [/code]
Is it possible if someone can check this out? The main class does exist at that location. I had to add zeros to the end of the name of the zip file because it would upload. So it does not mean anything.
Thanks.
